articles.title: WHO Defends China’s Repeated Coronavirus Diagnostic Changes Despite Hubei Health Official’s Complaints
articles.description: The World Health Organization defended China’s change to its coronavirus diagnostic process, despite a health official from China’s Hubei province claiming a lack of transparency

articles.title: 30-Year Treasury Yields Reflect Long-Term Economic Headwinds
articles.description: U.S. markets had performed well despite fears that coronavirus could disrupt global supply chains and hold back demand in key Asian markets. That changed Friday.
